ComicInfo.Summary:
The final confrontation that has been building for months - Calie versus her brother Johnny, the newly crowned sadistic Mad Hatter! New York City is the battleground for their final battle and when the smoke clears only one of them will be left among the living. Will Johnny's evil triumph over Calie and lead to the destruction of our world? The final issue to the smash hit series is here and it is not to be missed! Featuring covers by Wolverine: Origins artist Mike Deodato and Eric Basadula, shipping in a 50/50 ratio.
